Shri Ramswaroop Memorial College of Engineering and Management (SRMCEM) is a college in Lucknow, Uttar Pradesh, India SRMCEM is affiliated to Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam Technical University (AKTU) (previously Uttar Pradesh Technical University (UPTU)).
SRMCEM has been ranked among the top engineering colleges of the state, and its several of its alumni have been gold and silver medalists of the university. From the report of June 2018 some different news papers survey Ramswaroop College as the best college of Lucknow ranking 5th in AKTU.
